@{
    Layout = "_Layout";
    ViewData["Title"] = "Beach Resorts";
}

<div class="main-content">
    <h1>Beach Resorts</h1>
    <p>Here you can find a list of recommended beach resorts.</p>

    <section>
        <h2>Bodrum</h2>
        <div class="resort">
            <h3>Kempinski Hotel Barbaros Bay Bodrum</h3>
            <img src="~/images/infinity-pool-bodrum.jpg" alt="Kempinski Hotel Barbaros Bay">
            <p>Kempinski Hotel Barbaros Bay is one of the most luxurious hotels in Bodrum, known for its stunning sea views and private beach. The hotel offers spa facilities, various restaurants, and comfortable rooms.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Antalya</h2>
        <div class="resort">
            <h3>Rixos Premium Belek</h3>
            <img src="~/images/Rixos-Premium-Belek-beach.jpg" alt="Rixos Premium Belek">
            <img src="~/images/resort-rixos-antalya.jpg" alt="Rixos Premium Belek">
            <p>Located in the Belek area of Antalya, Rixos Premium Belek is famous for its wide beach, luxurious amenities, and various activity options. It is an ideal holiday destination for families and couples.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="resort">
            <h3>Regnum Carya Golf & Resort Hotel</h3>
            
            <img src="~/images/regnum-carya-golf-spa.jpg" alt="Regnum Carya Golf & Resort Hotel">
            <p>Regnum Carya, located in Belek, is famous for its golf courses, luxurious rooms, and wide beach. With high service quality and rich amenities, it is an excellent holiday center for families and couples.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Çeşme</h2>
        <div class="resort">
            <h3>Sheraton Cesme Hotel Resort & Spa</h3>
            <img src="~/images/sheraton-cesme-hotel-spa.jpg" alt="Sheraton Cesme Hotel Resort & Spa">
            <img src="~/images/sheraton-beach-cesme.jpg" alt="Sheraton Cesme Hotel Resort & Spa">
            <p>Sheraton Cesme, one of the most popular hotels in Çeşme, is located on Ilıca Beach. The hotel offers extensive spa facilities, indoor and outdoor swimming pools, and various restaurants for a comfortable holiday experience.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Marmaris</h2>
        <div class="resort">
            <h3>D Maris Bay</h3>
            <img src="~/images/dmarisbay-beach.jpg" alt="D Maris Bay">
            <p>Located in Marmaris, D Maris Bay features five different beaches, luxury restaurants, and extensive spa facilities. With its natural beauty and high service quality, it offers guests an unforgettable holiday experience.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Fethiye</h2>
        <div class="resort">
            <h3>Hillside Beach Club</h3>
            <img src="~/images/Hillside-Beach-Club.jpg" alt="Hillside Beach Club">
            <img src="~/images/Hillside-Beach-Club-havuz.jpg" alt="Hillside Beach Club">
            <p>Hillside Beach Club, located in Fethiye, is famous for its natural beauty and wide beach. Offering various water sports, activities, and luxurious amenities, it is an ideal holiday center for families and couples.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Ayvalık</h2>
        <div class="resort">
            <h3>Ortunc Hotel</h3>
            <img src="~/images/Ortunc_Hotel_spa.jpg" alt="Ortunc Hotel">
            <img src="~/images/ortunchotelspa-ayvalik.jpg" alt="Ortunc Hotel">
            <p>Ortunc Hotel, located on Cunda Island in Ayvalık, is a boutique hotel known for its stunning natural scenery, private beach, and tranquil atmosphere. It is ideal for those seeking a peaceful holiday.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="resort">
            <h3>D Resort Ayvalık</h3>
            <img src="~/images/d-resort-ayvalik.jpg" alt="D Resort Ayvalık">
            <img src="~/images/dresort-aksam-hotel.jpg" alt="D Resort Ayvalık">
            <p>Located within the natural beauty of Ayvalık, D Resort Ayvalık stands out with its modern design and comfortable rooms. The hotel offers a wide beach, various restaurants, and relaxation facilities for a pleasant holiday.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

